; Details the tower and the ritual.

Page_0: "The tower is the place. How lucky that it lies within the walls of my garden? No, it is more than luck. A greater design is at work, and all things are falling into place.

I have forbidden the guards from approaching the tower. If any were to disturb the ritual chamber, it could be ruinous. But all shall be well: its doors are locked and sturdy, and the only key resides here in my safe.

C.d.R."
